<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>David Suon Aksi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lalpa David leh a suon aksi chu,
 Na dikna gama di'n Nangin nei guot tai;
 Ka kipahna tuilien bangin a lien hi,
 Thih lui pangah Na min pakin la sa'ng ka.

[V2]
 Aw Lalpa zaila'n Na min chawian ka,
 Khawvela Na siemte'n lasau hen:
 Lalpa chawihat na'n aw chu suoh un,
 Lei chung hi pakna la'n dim ina.

[V3]
 2. Mihing ka hung hih ma'n le Lalpa Isu'n,
 Thisan in man dang ngek loin nei tan tai;
 A malin sim sengin gen thei ta leng chu,
 Na thilpiek te hi la hawih in phuong ingka.

[V4]
 3. Aw Lalpa, khawiah em mun nei guotsak chu,?
 Daniel bangin kawtcha awngah thil ingka;
 Sana khawtuol sungleh a In zephawih chu,
 Dahum ale khupdin bekin thil ingka.

[V5]
 4. Aw Immanuel lei leh van thak siem chu,
 A dung leh vailamah va en viel leu hing;
 Buoina tincheng thuoka I khensa teu chu,
 Van lopina tawh a meluh mu taitiu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>88</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
</song>